The paper deals with natural language labelling tasks, which suggests that it belongs to the category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The paper also proposes a probabilistic model that incorporates neural networks, which suggests that it may also belong to the categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper applies the proposed method to text classification and textual entailment, which suggests that it may also belong to the categories of Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
